The '''Bangladesh Jatiyatabadi Sramik Dal''' is a national [[trade union]] federation in [[Bangladesh]]. It is affiliated with the [[International Trade Union Confederation]].
BJSD is politically tied to the [[Bangladesh Nationalist Party]]. Anowar Hossain is the President of the federation and Nurul Islam Khan Nasim is the General Secretary. Its central Office is located in Noyapaltan, Dhaka.
